		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hmm, I checked on the config and the "pruning" was enabled.  It doesn't say how old a post had to be to be "pruned" though.  I disabled it.  I see at least the 'welcome' thread on the general board is still here, from Oct. 2004.

		

